The '''''Boltthrower''''' was an Imperial [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate]]. It was responding to an attack on a Cargo Transfer Area which the [[BFF-1 bulk freighter/Legends|BFF-1 bulk freighter]] ''[[Libom]]'', which carried new surveillance probes for the [[Relentless (Sunaj IV)|''Relentless'']], was disabled. Despite assistance from the [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] [[Scorpion (CR90 corvette)|''Scorpion'']] and the frigate's own [[TIE/IN interceptor/Legends|TIE/IN interceptors]] and [[TIE/sa tactical bomber/Legends|TIE/sa bombers]], the freighter was captured and the ''Scorpion'' was destroyed.

